{"id":215914,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/03/global-voices-刚果：爆炸带来愤怒与团结/","date":"2012-03-17T04:49:50Z","modified":"2012-03-17T04:49:50Z","title":"Global Voices | 刚果：爆炸带来愤怒与团结","content":"<p><p>2012年三月四日布拉萨市附近姆皮拉的一处弹药库发生爆炸，一天之后开始清点受害者人数。最近的几次调查结果死者人数在一百五十到两百之间不等，一千五百人受伤。爆炸带来茫然困惑已经开始被愤怒和团结意识取代。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.digitalcongo.net/\" href=\"http://www.digitalcongo.net/\">数位刚果</a>上关于媒体报导的评论中引用灯塔日报对事件的<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.digitalcongo.net/article/81947\" href=\"http://www.digitalcongo.net/article/81947\">详细报导</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>根据刚果政府官员表示，爆炸是由姆皮拉位于刚果河畔的装甲兵团军营弹药库的火灾所引起。部份当地居民仍被困在家中。总统办公室礼宾司长贝图．班加纳说明，姆皮拉一带已被摧毁。约数百人在爆炸中受伤。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/lebeization\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/lebeization\">Lebeization</a>在<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GKVoUgcf5pc&#038;context=C33c1316ADOEgsToPDskK3NVK8ZrkVumIec26FghbS\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GKVoUgcf5pc&#038;context=C33c1316ADOEgsToPDskK3NVK8ZrkVumIec26FghbS\">Youtube</a>上发布的影片纪录了其中一次爆炸的震撼：</p>\n<p> </p>\n</p>\n<p>储存在姆皮拉的弹药种类如 <a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=308942079167831&#038;set=a.308941852501187.74468.100001561242289&#038;type=3&#038;theater\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=308942079167831&#038;set=a.308941852501187.74468.100001561242289&#038;type=3&#038;theater\">Congo Futur Espoir</a> 脸书<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/media/set/?set=a.308941852501187.74468.100001561242289&#038;type=3\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/media/set/?set=a.308941852501187.74468.100001561242289&#038;type=3\">相簿</a>的这张照片所示：</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=308942079167831&#038;set=a.308941852501187.74468.100001561242289&#038;type=3&#038;theater\"><img title=\"Munitions Congo Brazzaville\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/Munitions-Congo-Brazzaville-261x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"261\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<p>据信是姆皮拉弹药库中储存的弹药 — 来自 Congo Futur Espoir 的脸书（经所有者同意公开）</p>\n</div>\n<p>在市中心存放这类军火正是民众愤怒的原因。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/nardello.ghislain\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nardello.ghislain\">Ghislain Nardello</a> 在<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/media/set/?set=a.308941852501187.74468.100001561242289&#038;type=1&#038;comment_id=3205133\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/media/set/?set=a.308941852501187.74468.100001561242289&#038;type=1&#038;comment_id=3205133\">脸书回应</a>中质疑：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>怎么会把武装部队的军火放在首都（布拉萨市）中心？这些不是该用来保卫国家抵御外侮的吗，而今天它们只造成刚果同胞的伤亡和公共与私人财产损失。国家一定要照料死伤者，赔偿受害家庭，重建他们的房屋。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/chancel.moussavou\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chancel.moussavou\">Chancel Moussavou</a> 继续<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=309019659160073&#038;set=a.308941852501187.74468.100001561242289&#038;type=1&#038;comment_id=764941\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=309019659160073&#038;set=a.308941852501187.74468.100001561242289&#038;type=1&#038;comment_id=764941\">表示</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>这就是满脑子只有武器的后果。花在军火上的钱本来可以拿来建造学校、医院或是补助企业。发生这种意外之后要大家怎么能有安全感？说实话，太可悲了！</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/Patrickericmampouya\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/Patrickericmampouya\">Patrick Eric Mampouya</a> 分享的这段刚果国家电视台<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1nKMmfGpnzE&#038;feature=youtu.be&#038;a\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1nKMmfGpnzE&#038;feature=youtu.be&#038;a\">影片</a>纪录了目前人满为患的医院情景：</p>\n</p>\n<p>刚果民众开始为受到影响的家庭亲友组织搜救和救济团。巴黎的非政府组织非洲发展协会发起<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.congomaboke.com/?p=10489\" href=\"http://www.congomaboke.com/?p=10489\">呼吁</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>因情况紧急，我们希望为现场搜救队提供支援；请捐助紧急急救用品，包括急救箱、绷带、消毒药水、简易手术工具、敷布、药品……</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>刚果民众也正透过为布拉萨市成立的<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/congobrazza/posts/10150598262930847\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/congobrazza/posts/10150598262930847\">脸书页面</a>动员救灾人力资源。</p>\n<div>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Yenrong\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80E5%88%9A%E6%9E%9C%EF%BC%9A%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%E5%B8%A6%E6%9D%A5%E6%84%A4%E6%80%92%E4%B8%8E%E5%9B%A2%E7%BB%93&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F03%2F17%2F10602%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F03%2F17%2F10602%2F&#038;desc=%E5%88%9A%E6%9E%9C%EF%BC%9A%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%E5%B8%A6%E6%9D%A5%E6%84%A4%E6%80%92%E4%B8%8E%E5%9B%A2%E7%BB%93\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F03%2F17%2F10602%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F03%2F17%2F10602%2F&#038;text=%E5%88%9A%E6%9E%9C%EF%BC%9A%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%E5%B8%A6%E6%9D%A5%E6%84%A4%E6%80%92%E4%B8%8E%E5%9B%A2%E7%BB%93&#038;via=globalvoiceszh\" title=\"twitter\"><span>twitter</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://reddit.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F03%2F17%2F10602%2F&#038;title=%E5%88%9A%E6%9E%9C%EF%BC%9A%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%E5%B8%A6%E6%9D%A5%E6%84%A4%E6%80%92%E4%B8%8E%E5%9B%A2%E7%BB%93\" title=\"reddit\"><span>reddit</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.stumbleupon.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2